<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:14:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶伦称七国集团将讨论应对中国产能过剩问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-g7-discuss-responses-chinas-excess-industrial-capacity-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国财长耶伦周四表示，七国集团财长将讨论他们对中国工业产能过剩的担忧以及可能的应对措施，并补充说，如果北京不做出政策改变，他们的经济将受到大量廉价中国商品的打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-g7-discuss-responses-chinas-excess-industrial-capacity-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>亿滋国际因跨境贸易限制被欧盟罚款 3.657 亿欧元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-fined-3657-mln-euros-by-eu-cross-border-trade-curbs-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，奥利奥制造商亿滋国际因阻碍欧盟国家之间巧克力、饼干和咖啡产品的跨境贸易而被欧盟反垄断监管机构处以 3.375 亿欧元（3.6572 亿美元）的罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-fined-3657-mln-euros-by-eu-cross-border-trade-curbs-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国国家库存计划购买多达 15,000 吨钴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-state-stockpiler-aims-buy-up-15000-t-cobalt-sources-say-2024-05-23/</link><description>三名知情人士告诉路透社，中国计划在未来几个月内从中国本土生产商购买最多 15,000 吨钴金属作为国内库存，并补充说，这将是单次采购的创纪录数量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 08:46:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-state-stockpiler-aims-buy-up-15000-t-cobalt-sources-say-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国飞机制造商中国商飞瞄准沙特阿拉伯进行全球扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-planemaker-comac-eyes-saudi-arabia-global-expansion-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国飞机制造商中国商飞公司正将沙特阿拉伯视为其国际野心的跳板，这家国有公司加大了海外销售力度，打入由西方制造商主导的客机市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 08:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-planemaker-comac-eyes-saudi-arabia-global-expansion-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国的粮食安全梦想面临土地、土壤和水的困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-food-security-dream-faces-land-soil-water-woes-2024-05-23/</link><description>专家表示，作为全球最大的农产品进口国，中国已制定目标，在未来十年大幅减少对海外采购的依赖，以促进粮食安全，但实现这些目标将极其困难。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 06:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-food-security-dream-faces-land-soil-water-woes-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、中国、日本将于5月26日至27日举行四年来首次峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-hold-summit-seoul-may-26-27-reports-yonhap-2024-05-23/</link><description>首尔青瓦台周四表示，韩国、中国和日本领导人将于5月26日至27日在首尔举行四年多来的首次三边峰会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 05:44:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-hold-summit-seoul-may-26-27-reports-yonhap-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国联想延续收入增长势头，超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-lenovo-extends-revenue-growth-streak-beats-expectations-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国联想集团周四公布第四季度营收增长 9%，达到 138 亿美元，这家全球最大的个人电脑 (PC) 制造商摆脱了 COVID-19 大流行后的需求低迷。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 04:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-lenovo-extends-revenue-growth-streak-beats-expectations-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>有关中国在台湾周边进行军事演习的关键引述</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，中国在台湾周围开始为期两天的惩罚性演习，并称这是对“分裂主义行为”的回应，以及台湾新总统赖清德发表就职演说后，台湾军方动员了军队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 04:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/reactions-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国将军称中国军队于2023年进行了入侵台湾演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</link><description>一名驻该地区的美国高级将领周四表示，中国 2023 年在台湾海峡举行的军事演习演练了入侵该岛的关键演习，尽管实际的攻击并非迫在眉睫或不可避免。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-practiced-taiwan-invasion-manoeuvres-2023-says-us-general-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达股价上涨；投资者对利率持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，人工智能典范英伟达的业绩引发科技股上涨，全球股市小幅上涨，不过利率可能维持在较高水平的时间可能长于许多人预期的前景削弱了一些投资者的乐观情绪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>哈尔滨疑似瓦斯爆炸造成1人死亡3人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</link><description>官方媒体周四称，中国东北城市哈尔滨一栋住宅楼发生疑似瓦斯爆炸，炸毁阳台，造成一人死亡、三人受伤，瓦砾散落在街上。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-apartment-building-chinas-harbin-says-state-media-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美联储会议纪要鹰派，美元接近一周高点；英镑对选举消息无动于衷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，美元兑一篮子货币创下本月最大单日百分比涨幅，周四徘徊在一周高点附近，原因是上次美联储会议纪要显示一些官员愿意加息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-highest-week-after-hawkish-fed-minutes-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在台湾周边展开“惩罚”兵棋推演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</link><description>愤怒的中国周四在台湾周围发起了“惩罚”演习，据称这是对“分裂主义行为”的回应，在官方媒体谴责新就职的总统赖清德之际，派出全副武装的战机并进行模拟袭击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>桥水基金任命中国区总裁阿尔珀特负责监管新投资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</link><description>桥水基金已提拔其中国区总经理乔安娜·阿尔珀特 (Joanna Alpert) 担任最近成立的业务部门负责人，该部门专注于管理和创造新的投资产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，因国家监管机构审查而推迟波音向中国交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位知情人士告诉路透社，由于中国对驾驶舱录音机电池进行监管审查，波音向中国的飞机交付最近几周被推迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>